            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間10日09:56，深證成指上漲279.96點（或2%），暫報14276.22點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+3.78%</li><li>近 1 月：-0.51%</li><li>近 3 月：-0.88%</li><li>近 6 月：+1.97%</li><li>今年以來：+3.48%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>語音技術概念領漲+3.64%。其中    全誌科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300458:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300458\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300458-CN</a>)            上漲        13.24%            ;        *ST華聞(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:000793:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/000793\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">000793-CN</a>)            上漲        4.96%            ;        漢威科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300007:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300007\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300007-CN</a>)            上漲        1.66%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>參股銀行概念領漲+2.55%。其中    蒙草生態(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300355:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300355\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300355-CN</a>)            上漲        15.89%            ;        永清環保(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300187:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://